## Automate The Boring Things! CH6 String Manipulations

* Escape Characters
* In & Not In Operators for strings

#### String Methods
* upper()
* lower()
<br>
True if,
* isupper() - at least on string letter is uppercase
* islower() - at least on string letter is lowercase

#### isX String Methods
True if,
* isalpha() - only lowercase & not blank
* isalnum() - only num, letters, & not blank
* isdecimal() - only numerica chars & not blank
* isspace() - only spaces, tabs, new-lines, & not blank

**use these methods to validate user input**
#### More string methods
* startswith()
* endswith()
* join()
* split()

#### Justifying text
* rjust()
* ljust()
* center()

#### Removing Whitespace
* strip()
* rstrip()
* lstrip()
